sections.Trivia:
- Naeko is seen at the karaoke box singing closing 60 and closing 61.
- The unknown man's van is an effect blue metallic 2006 Honda Mobilio Spike [GK].
- The vehicle in the last episode is a 2018 Honda N-VAN [JJ].
- Kazunobu Chiba's grand tourer sports car is an ultimate silver 2017 Nissan GT-R [R35]. The license plate number is 新宿 351, ち 6-26 (Shinjuku 351, Chi 6-26).
- Conan recognizes Twinkle Twinkle Little Star lyric from hearing 4 sets of 7-times tapping on the phone, and can sing this song very well and on key.
- The name of the characters come from colours and numbers[1]:
- Shiori Yagi (八木 紫織) comes from purple (紫) and eight (8, 八);
- Toko Momosaki (百崎 橙子) comes from orange (橙色) and hundred (100, 百);
- Kengo Aono (青野 健吾) comes from blue (青) and five (5, 五);
- Manji Akamine (赤峰 萬治) comes from red (赤) and ten thousand (10 000, 萬);
- Yuzo Shiroyama (白山 裕三) comes from white (白) and three (3, 三);
- Aiko Midorikawa (緑川 藍子) comes from green (緑) and indigo (藍);
- Additionally, blue, red and white are colors of traffic violation tickets.
